{"type": "article", "id": 49423, "title": "分拣谷物的传统簸箕，也能变成座椅｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-01-22T23:15:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 8331, "name": "吱音"}, {"id": 26039, "name": "Seletti"}, {"id": 6996, "name": "Studio Job"}, {"id": 23855, "name": "Pelle"}, {"id": 8926, "name": "Tom Dixon"}, {"id": 46652, "name": "Stefan Diez"}, {"id": 47206, "name": "Hiroyuki Morita"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 108, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180119231932UEt75PAduf2DL48x.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} </style>  </p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>磨彩系列抱枕 by 吱音</h3><p>水磨石，是传统的工艺技术，将碎石、玻璃拌入水泥，随着喜好改变调色与拼花，很常出现在记忆里的老宅。最近，独立家居设计品牌吱音把水磨石元素融入抱枕设计中，方形抱枕的大小为 60 x 60cm，刚好是一个成人双臂得以紧紧环抱的尺寸。长方体抱枕的大小为 26 x 43cm，以及 12cm 的厚度，放置于家中的长椅上，可以倚靠、可以枕躺；亦可成为办公室椅子的最佳伴侣。</p><p>磨彩系列抱枕具有高度回弹力的枕芯永远保持蓬松柔软。外层的枕套具有细腻而滑顺的质感，天然质朴的肌理，一如水磨石那般。灰白两色为主色调，缀以活泼的鹅黄色，让你简单纯朴的家居生活，依旧充满温馨欢快设计感。售价 129 至 159 元，<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.1-c-s.w5003-17549343977.3.3a56fc0cGhfUxD&amp;id=563027572955&amp;scene=taobao_shop\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232050wsU3CG5YEk7IeMAa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.611028\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232050N0Qkx4tVfgIri1wX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.605381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232050jX2aSMc0sTRhpNW4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.602699\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232051qtMXQigyO4WU3zS2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.795960\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018011923205250Ko7JBTwNeZmYfE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646269\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Felix by Studio Job for Seletti</h3><p>创意二人组 Studio Job 与米兰设计品牌 Seletti，最近推出了合作项目 Felix，一款猫咪形状的灯具。这是一款实际猫咪尺寸的灯具，灵感来源于设计师自己养的小猫。设计师复制了猫咪体态的每个细节，共有三种不同版本可供选择，分别是黑猫款、白猫款和黑白花猫款。猫咪灯展示出放松的状态，其尾巴高高竖起，尾巴下藏着 USB 接口、开关与调光器。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232115zoYUjvJrdM4lIh6w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232115FP8urNbaOc3W2gDQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232115NXiyIJzghoMTp6GZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232115FdJQxTvk3rHswf0j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/studio-job-felix-seletti-01-17-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Super Texture Collection by Tom Dixon</h3><p>在最近的巴黎家居装饰博览会上，英国设计师 Tom Dixon 推出一系列纺织品，意在探索织造、编织、打结和数字印刷技术。Super Texture 系列包含一系列的坐垫和抱枕，有的是大胆的饱和度较高的色块的碰撞，有的是以抽象的城市景观为特色，有的是以地质元素为灵感。</p><p>印度北部瓦拉纳西的工匠们使用通常用来制作地毯的手工簇绒技术来制作这一系列产品。 Tom Dixon 说，他的灵感源自 1970 年代的嬉皮壁画。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232203T8esuOFG7fjU9LVh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232204GjPgnmYcNQRpZdst.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499577\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232207EH450GYk3bh6QCRe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499577\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232208coATfNICQ5uxY6jU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499577\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232236uvY7GPJDkRpLrzKZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/01/19/tom-dixon-tufted-printed-embroidered-textile-collection-maison-objet/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Tripp Mini Lighting by Pelle</h3><p>纽约设计品牌 Pelle 在最近的多伦多室内设计展上推出了一系列小型吊灯和壁灯，由三角形金属框架包裹，可以向不同方向散射光线。 Tripp Mini 系列是原先 Tripp 系列的延伸，比如三角形框架的沿用，但新版本尺寸较小，可以在更广泛的空间中使用。</p><p>Pelle 的创始人 Jean 和 Oliver Pelle 表示：“我们有兴趣在更具雕塑感的形式下操纵光线。当光从构成三角形的金属片中逐渐散发出来的时候，光就软化了，辐射到周围的地板和墙壁上。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232453B1saxhN0SyP5zlq3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232454etYZ4Myr6bQPFw23.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714202\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232454a6Muoc4U9kjsynXD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000846\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232455yj1mxvASH49RteJB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232455RGVosK4ChTN5J8Db.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/01/18/pelle-tripp-mini-pendant-sconce-lighting-weathered-steel-fins-interior-design-show-ids-toronto/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>KIRI by Stefan Diez</h3><p>在上周的科隆国际家具展上，日本家具品牌 MEETEE 推出了 KIRI 系列橱柜，出自德国设计师 Stefan Diez 之手。2016 年，Stefan Diez 去过一次日本广岛，当地的传统和服收纳柜给予他很大启发。</p><p>这一次，他想赋予这种传统橱柜更现代的表现形式，既能够展示泡桐木的特色，又能够赋予其更有韵味的色彩。最特别的是，柜门可以保持在任何位置打开。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232545YC836G1FUnAzqOkW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672372\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232601ML0Z9uN827fUaOBe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672372\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232601eBd6LbYDuJn54Moj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672372\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801192326015fehkUtMnX2qCcTP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.794621\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232602LYWMKjIriStNmk38.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.794621\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232602fnQS9bMADo6eTwdZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672372\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/imm-cologne-2018-stefan-diez-office-meetee-kiri-01-19-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Temi &amp; Cellastic Chair by Hiroyuki Morita</h3><p>同样是在今年的科隆国际家具展上，日本设计实践工作室 Rope 的创始人 Hiroyuki Morita 推出了两把特别的、风格鲜明的椅子，以一种纯粹的自然形式。Temi 椅重新诠释了曾经用于分拣谷物的传统工具，被简化为一个座椅。Cellastic 椅是一个偏现代化的制造实验，它由乳胶和尼龙线制成，后者控制前者的弹性支撑坐着的人。它的背部有一个连续的波浪图案。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232659OUX5lypcJ39YjbHK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.771394\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232659Yc5rxo07jiHLqyvn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232659sZTYhPQdblFLn6AM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.099022\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232659csbFMtPnrHWN6CoE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660955\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232659FE9cM6ykvq8fmxlY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.770171\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119232659weWhgVpbomsrSLkf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654835\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/imm-cologne-2018-hiroyuki-morita-01-18-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}